node.text:
We’re trying out a new way to provide some updates on what’s new with NovelKeys. 

In this Updates with Mike we feature: 
-Mute Jades
-Website Revamp
-Games
-The Keyboard Meetup
-PBT Milkshake
-Aluvia 
-NK87 - Entry Edition

More details will be announced once they’re available. Stay tuned!

node.text: Meet the other Mike. He loves cardboard boxes, string, tape, twine, snacks and ear scratches. It's no wonder he excels on the fulfillment team! When he's at home he epitomizes every aspect of the modern day Cat Dad by making sure his fur babies Rize and Ezra want for nothing. If you don't like cats, we blame you.

We are so glad to be a part of the downtown Morgantown business community and appreciate the warm welcome from @mainstreetmorgantown! 

#dowtownmorgantown #novelkeys #morgantownwv

node.text: Meet Derek. A connoisseur of MP3s and ETFs alike, he is well versed in the songs of the market. When he's not churning out LPs or checking his index funds, he heads up our customer service. Please stop blaming him for everything.
